verbose_text: Representative images of Hsp27 expression were shown in Fig. XREF_FIG C. Patients with high expression of Hsp27 exhibited worse overall survival (median overall survival time, 30.0 and 51.7 months, respectively; P < 0.001) and shorter time to recurrence (median time to recurrence, 18.0 and 46.7 months, respectively; P < 0.01) than patients with low expression of Hsp27.
